### Entity Configuration

Use Fluent API in separate configuration classes. Follow the data model conventions: UUIDs as primary keys, `decimal` for money fields.

```csharp
// Data/Configurations/CampConfiguration.cs
public class CampConfiguration : IEntityTypeConfiguration<Camp>
{
    public void Configure(EntityTypeBuilder<Camp> builder)
    {
        builder.HasKey(c => c.Id);
        builder.Property(c => c.Id).HasDefaultValueSql("gen_random_uuid()");

        builder.Property(c => c.Name)
            .IsRequired()
            .HasMaxLength(200);

        builder.Property(c => c.PricePerPerson)
            .HasPrecision(10, 2);

        builder.Property(c => c.Status)
            .HasConversion<string>()
            .HasMaxLength(20);

        builder.HasMany(c => c.Registrations)
            .WithOne(r => r.Camp)
            .HasForeignKey(r => r.CampId)
            .OnDelete(DeleteBehavior.Restrict);
    }
}
```

### Migrations

- **Version Control**: All database changes must go through EF Core migrations
- **Descriptive Names**: Use descriptive migration names
- **Review Before Applying**: Always review generated migration files

```bash
# Create a new migration
dotnet ef migrations add AddCampCapacityField --project src/Abuvi.API

# Apply migrations
dotnet ef database update --project src/Abuvi.API

# Generate SQL script for production
dotnet ef migrations script --idempotent --project src/Abuvi.API
```

### Repository Pattern

Each feature defines its own repository interface and implementation:

```csharp
// Repository interface — in the feature folder
public interface ICampsRepository
{
    Task<Camp?> GetByIdAsync(Guid id, CancellationToken ct);
    Task<IReadOnlyList<Camp>> GetAllAsync(CancellationToken ct);
    Task<IReadOnlyList<Camp>> GetByStatusAsync(CampStatus status, CancellationToken ct);
    Task AddAsync(Camp camp, CancellationToken ct);
    Task UpdateAsync(Camp camp, CancellationToken ct);
    Task DeleteAsync(Guid id, CancellationToken ct);
}

// Implementation — also in the feature folder
public class CampsRepository(AbuviDbContext db) : ICampsRepository
{
    public async Task<Camp?> GetByIdAsync(Guid id, CancellationToken ct)
        => await db.Camps
            .AsNoTracking()
            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(c => c.Id == id, ct);

    public async Task<IReadOnlyList<Camp>> GetByStatusAsync(CampStatus status, CancellationToken ct)
        => await db.Camps
            .AsNoTracking()
            .Where(c => c.Status == status)
            .OrderByDescending(c => c.StartDate)
            .ToListAsync(ct);

    public async Task UpdateAsync(Camp camp, CancellationToken ct)
    {
        db.Camps.Update(camp);
        await db.SaveChangesAsync(ct);
    }
}
```

