### Test Organization

- Place test files in a structure mirroring the source code
- Use separate projects for unit and integration tests
- Use xUnit with FluentAssertions and NSubstitute

```text
Abuvi.Tests/
├── Unit/
│   └── Features/
│       ├── Camps/
│       │   ├── CampsServiceTests.cs
│       │   ├── CampsEndpointsTests.cs
│       │   └── CreateCampValidatorTests.cs
│       └── Registrations/
